author: Max Margan For Daily Mail Australia
title: Carwoola bushfire continues to burn | Daily Mail Online
text: Kangaroos and livestock left stranded on scorched fireground as horror bushfire wreaks havoc in NSW destroying at least 15 homes and charring more than 3,500 hectares The blaze at Carwoola, near Canberra, has blackened more than 3,500 hectares Fire, which is still out of control, is believed to have destroyed up to 15 homes Heartbreaking images show kangaroos and horses roaming the scorched earth Families were forced to flee as they watched their homes go up in flames 100 new fires began after a band of electrical storms swept NSW on Friday Published: 22:38 GMT, 17 February 2017 | Updated: 02:46 GMT, 18 February 2017 123 shares
